================================================================================

RECOMMENDED OPTIONS:

1. Heroku + MongoDB Atlas
   - Free/Paid tier available
   - Easy deployment
   - Good for learning

2. AWS EC2 + MongoDB Atlas
   - Highly scalable
   - Professional option
   - Pay-as-you-go pricing

3. DigitalOcean + MongoDB Atlas
   - Budget-friendly
   - Good performance
   - Simple deployment

4. Vercel (Frontend) + Railway (Backend)
   - Modern approach
   - Fast deployments
   - Affordable

5. Self-hosted Server
   - Complete control
   - One-time investment
   - Requires maintenance

